  <brief_title>Nursing-Home Residents Given Bread Fortified With Vitamin D3</brief_title>
  <official_title>Long-Term Effects of Giving Nursing-Home Residents Bread Fortified With 125 Micrograms (5000 IU) Vitamin D3 Per Daily Serving</official_title>
